                            <comment id="14474612" author="melix" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2013 11:44:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This bug shows that the inferred type after a switch is wrong. Switch should be considered as an improved &quot;if&quot; statement, which is it not here. Not specific to &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt; though.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
